":"周末去龙岗的咖啡店探店，喝完咖啡看到外面阳光很好，查地图发现附近有个龙潭公园，于是就过去闲逛了。本以为只是普通公园，到了发现面积挺大的，没想到这么好拍！！！[赞R]\n\t\n公园有很多花花草草和树木，有个大湖，湖面波光粼粼，锦鲤在水中悠哉悠哉地游来游去。湖中间有座古风小楼，还有拱桥，感觉很适合拍汉服，有机会还要再来这拍拍汉服。[自拍R]\n\t\n而且龙潭公园好像都是龙岗附近的居民来，人比较少，不要老去中心公园香蜜公园人挤人了，来这里吧[偷笑R]\n\t\n地点：深圳市龙岗区龙潭公园\n交通：地铁16号线尚景站，步行10分钟\n附近有很多商场和咖啡店，不用担心吃喝哦[吧唧R]\n\t\n拍照设备：索尼A7R5，70200GM2\n#春天就要逛公园 #深圳拍照 #深圳周末去哪儿 #深圳古风拍照地 #深圳汉服约拍 #深圳溜娃好去处 #正是人间四月天 #深圳公园 #深圳龙岗拍照打卡 ","resource-id":"com.xingin.xhs:id\/chg","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.xingin.xhs","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 998, 1190)","boundsInScreen":"(41, 1863 - 1039, 2400)"},{"index":4,"text":"编辑于 04-18 广东","resource-id":"com.xingin.xhs:id\/eil","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.xingin.xhs","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 998, 35)","boundsInScreen":"(41, 3095 - 1039, 2400)"},{"index":5,"text":"共 10条评论","resource-id":"com.xingin.xhs:id\/eh1","class":"android.widget.TextView","package":"com.xingin.xhs","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":false,"enabled":true,"focusable":false,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 189, 55)","boundsInScreen":"(41, 3227 - 230, 2400)"},{"index":6,"resource-id":"com.xingin.xhs:id\/bx","class":"android.widget.RelativeLayout","package":"com.xingin.xhs","checkable":false,"checked":false,"clickable":true,"enabled":true,"focusable":true,"focused":false,"scrollable":false,"long-clickable":false,"password":false,"selected":false,"boundsInParent":"(0, 0 - 1080, 143)","boundsInScreen":"(0, 3282 - 1080, 2400)","children":[{"index":0,"text":"说点什么吧，万一火了呢~","resource-id":"com.xingin.xhs:id\/eh2","class":"andro